Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,神父 到目前 你应该很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come now, Father, you should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里并不欢迎你 特别是今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're not welcome here, and especially not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我没时间再跟你争论\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've got no time to start old arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只要一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We want only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这座房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要这座房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You want the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会接管这房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We will take the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不连我老婆也接管得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Would you like my wife while you're at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们不靠边站 我们只好强制夺下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If you won't stand aside, then we'll take it by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用什么夺 上帝之手吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And by what power? The hand of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,用拳头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the fist of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}In the name of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那里面是什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么 帆布下是什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What is it? What's under the canvas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,神父 回答我 那是什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Father, answer me. What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,愿上帝原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}May God forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这件怎么样 还行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What do you think of this? Will it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在70年代末期 这么穿还不如套个垃圾袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The late 1970s? You'd be better off in a bin bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 听听这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold on, listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,伊恩·杜瑞和木头人 1979年第一热门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ian Dury and The Blockheads. Number one in 1979.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个朋克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're a punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你的类型了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's what you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一个混合了乡村摇滚乐风格的老朋克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's what you are, a big old punk with a bit of rockabilly thrown in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去看看他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you want to go and see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说去演唱会吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How do you mean, in concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不然要塔迪斯做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What else is the Tardis for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我能带你去特拉法尔加战役\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can take you to the Battle of Trafalgar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第一届反重力奥运会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the First Antigravity Olympics,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒穿越卢比肯河\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Caesar crossing the Rubicon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,或者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}or...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去1979年11月21日 看伊恩·杜瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ian Dury at the Top Rank, Sheffield,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在地球-英格兰-谢菲尔德市的演唱会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}England, Earth, 21st November 1979,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就谢菲尔德好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sheffield it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊……着陆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,1979年 见鬼的一年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}1979! Hell of a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,中国入侵越南\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}China invades Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,《布偶大电影》我喜欢这部电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Muppet Movie, love that film.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特·撒切尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Margaret Thatcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,SKYLAB卫星着陆 我帮了点忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Skylab falls to Earth with a little help from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,差点要了我的拇指 我爱我的拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nearly took off my thumb, and I like my thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要我的拇指 我很依赖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I need my thumb. I'm very attached to..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}my thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,1879年 半斤八两\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}1879. Same difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,解释一下你的来路\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You will explain your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,以及这个女子为何穿着暴露\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and the nakedness of this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是在苏格兰吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are we in Scotland?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能连这个都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How can you be ignorant of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我有点眼花缭乱 糊涂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm dazed and confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在跋山涉水的追踪这个暴露的丫头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've been chasing this wee naked child over hill and over dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧…你这个野姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Isn't that right, you timorous beastie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Och, aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在外面蹦跶\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've been "oot" and "aboot."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别用这种调调\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hoots, mon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不 真的别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, really don't. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,说明一下你的身份 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Will you identify yourself, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是詹姆斯·麦克里蒙博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm Doctor James McCrimmon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来自巴拉莫瑞小镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}from the township of Balamory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我有证书 我能否\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have my credentials, if I may?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见 爱丁堡大学的博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}As you can see, a doctorate from the University of Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是贝尔博士的学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I trained under Doctor Bell himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}WOMAN: Let them approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为那是明智之举 夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't think that's wise, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let them approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以靠近马车了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You will approach the carriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,表现出应有的尊敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and show all due deference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你介绍维多利亚女王殿下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}might I introduce Her Majesty Queen Victoria,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,印度女皇 "信仰捍卫者"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Empress of India and Defender of the Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是洛斯·泰勒 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose Tyler, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…我穿得那么少\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And my apologies for being so naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我有五个女儿 这对我来说没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've had five daughters. It's nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但你 博士 给我看看这些证书\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But you, Doctor, show me these credentials.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不早说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why didn't you say so immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这很清楚地写着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It states clearly here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大市长指定你为我的保护者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that you have been appointed by the Lord Provost as my protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 是的没错 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Does it? Yes, it does. Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那么容我问问\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Erm, then let me ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么陛下由陆路旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}why is Your Majesty travelling by road
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有条直达阿伯丁的铁路吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}when there's a train all the way to Aberdeen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,铁路上有棵树\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A tree on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是意外吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大不列颠及爱尔兰联合王国的女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I am the Queen of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,和我有关的事情都不会是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Everything around me tends to be planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有人企图刺杀吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}An assassination attempt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 真的吗 有人想要刺杀你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What, seriously? There's people out to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我都习惯于被人用枪筒瞄着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm quite used to staring down the barrel of a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特·麦克利什爵士就住在十英里外\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert MacLeish lives but 10 miles hence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经先通传过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We've sent word ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他会招待我们一晚 然后我们明天将抵达巴尔摩洛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He'll shelter us for tonight, then we can reach Balmoral tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这博士和他的"野丫头"将随同我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This Doctor and his timorous beastie will come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}{\i1}Yes, ma'am.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好继续前进 天快黑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We'd better get moving. It's almost nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 而且这里有很多关于狼的传说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Indeed, and there are stories of wolves in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都是些虚构的故事 用来吓唬小孩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fanciful tales, intended to scare the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但我认为有助血液循环 启程\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but good for the blood, I think. Drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,挺有趣的 因为说起刺杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's funny, though, 'cause you say assassination,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,人们通常会想起肯尼迪事件 而不是她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and you just think of Kennedy and stuff, not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,1879年 她已经遭遇过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}1879? She's had,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,六次刺杀企图了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}six attempts on her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我跟你说件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And I'll tell you something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚见了维多利亚女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We just met Queen Victoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What a laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她就坐在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She was just sitting there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,跟邮票一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Like a stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让她说"这并不好笑"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I want her to say, "We are not amused."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,和你赌五镑 我能让她说这句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet you 5 quid I can make her say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我跟你赌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, if I gambled on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是在滥用时间旅行者的特权\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it would be an abuse of my privilege as a traveller in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,十镑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}10 quid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,成交\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这么做 这是叛国\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't do this. It's treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那你妻子就会承受你的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then your wife will suffer the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 罗伯特爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Believe me, Sir Robert,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她会被吞噬的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}she will be devoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉因为紧急事件打搅到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My apologies for the emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎贝尔夫人怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And how is Lady Isobel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不太舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}indisposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她已出发去爱丁堡住一个季节\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm afraid She's gone to Edinburgh for the season,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她把厨师也带走了 厨房的储蓄都快没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and she's taken the cook with her, the kitchens are barely stocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您不愿屈身下住 我能理解 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wouldn't blame Your Majesty if you wanted to ride on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用这样想 我已饱尝乘车之旅了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not at all. I've had quite enough carriage exercise,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这里挺迷人的 很质朴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and this is charming, if rustic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次拜访这房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's my first visit to this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我前夫经常提起这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My late husband spoke of it often,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,火炬木之馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the Torchwood Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可以进去了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, shall we go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅这裸露的女子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And please excuse the naked girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个野孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's a feral. child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我在旧伦敦镇花六便士买来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bought her for sixpence in old London town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不买她也只能买到四不像了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was her or the Elephant Man, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得自己挺搞笑的 但我觉得并不好笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thinks he's funny, but I'm so not amused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为呢 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What do you think, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这无关紧要 我们能先进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It hardly matters. Shall we proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克森和拉姆齐 你们来护送这物品 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mackeson and Ramsay, you will escort the property. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那里面是什么东西啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So what's in there, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,皇家的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Property of the Crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能乱打主意 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You will dismiss any further thoughts, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的人 到后面去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The rest of you, go to the rear of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,按指定就位\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Assume the designated positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听到命令了 就位\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You heard the orders, positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,用你们的生命来守护好它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Guard it with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜这就是著名的"奋进号"了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This, I take it, is the famous endeavour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我父亲的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All my father's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在他晚年亲手建造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Built by hand in his final years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他渐渐沉迷其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It became something of an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他花在这上面的钱 比花在房子和自己身上的还多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He spent his money on this, rather than caring for the house or himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望能见到他 我喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wish I'd met him. I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西好漂亮 我能不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That thing's beautiful, can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请自便\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他在仿造什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What did he model it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我对这些一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 我们大部分人都觉得他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}To be honest, most of us thought him a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,精神失常吧 可以说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}shall we say, eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我希望能花多点时间陪陪他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wish now I'd spent more time with him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,倾听他的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and listened to his stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这有点糟糕啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's a bit rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面装了多少棱镜 太多了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How many prisms has it got? Way too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这放大倍率实在是太过了 真是个愚蠢之举\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The magnification's gone right over the top. That's a stupid kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是又很没礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Am I being rude again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是造型很不错 非常\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's pretty, very...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,精美\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,并且其想象力很值得称赞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And the imagination of it should be applauded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你不会赞成 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hmm. I thought you might disapprove, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,夜观天象 是不是有些天方夜谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stargazing. Isn't that a bit fanciful?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能觉得不好笑…之类的 没有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You could easily not be amused, or something. No?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这装置是用来观察广阔无穷的造物的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This device surveys the infinite work of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么比这更出色的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What could be finer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特爵士的父亲是我们的榜样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert's father was an example to us all,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他博学多识 在天文学和自然科学方面成就很高\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}a polymath, steeped in astronomy and the sciences,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,同时对民间传说和童话故事也很有研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}yet equally well-versed in folklore and fairytales.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,星空和魔法 我越来越喜欢他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stars and magic. I like him more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我前夫很喜欢与他作伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my late husband enjoyed his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔伯特王子本身对乡间迷信很感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Prince Albert himself was acquainted with many rural superstitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好像他就来自萨克森-科堡似的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}coming as he did from Saxe-Coburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是巴伐利亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's Bavaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,当阿尔伯特听说你们当地狼的故事时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}When Albert was told about your local wolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他欣喜不已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}he was transported.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这只狼是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So what's this wolf, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个故事而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就说来听听\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then tell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,传说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了 阁下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也许陛下的故事还是回房再说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Perhaps Her Majesty's party could repair to their rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在天色已晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's almost dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 是的 当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Of course. Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就用餐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And then supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,能找些衣服给这位泰勒小姐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And could we find some clothes for Miss Tyler?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我都快看烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm tired of nakedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不好玩 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not amusing, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特阁下 你妻子一定留了些衣服 找找看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert, your wife must have left some clothes. See to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们七点用餐 然后再多讲讲狼的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We shall dine at 7:00, and talk some more of this wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 今晚是个月圆之夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}After all, there is a full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So there is, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们悄无声息地进入这房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They came through the house in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把管家 主人和女主人都带走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They took the steward and the master, and my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我有个朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Listen, I've got a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫做博士 他知道该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's called the Doctor. He'll know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你得跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've got to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, but I can't, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,弗洛拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,弗洛拉 我们会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Flora, we'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,楼下来了很多人 还有许多士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's more people arrived downstairs, soldiers and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能帮我们 我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They can help us. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 好吗 跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on. Okay? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 小姐 我提醒过你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, Miss, I did warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他没死 我觉得没死 他一定被下药了之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's not dead, I don't think. He must be drugged or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的同伴说抱歉 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your companion begs an apology, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她的衣着稍微耽误了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Her clothing has somewhat delayed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 给她留点火腿好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, that's all right. Save her a wee bit of ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那野孩子可能连生肉都能吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The feral child could probably eat it raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,非常机智 陛下 非常幽默\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Very wise, ma'am. Very witty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,略微有点吧 只能说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Slightly witty, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很少机会能和我进餐 队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know you rarely get the chance to dine with me, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但不要显得太兴奋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是少机智一点 以防你呛到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I shall contain my wit in case I do you further injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 陛下 抱歉 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, ma'am. Sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都在等罗伯特爵士 来吧 爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Besides, we're all waiting on Sir Robert. Come, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你答应过要讲一个梦魇般的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You promised us a tale of nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}VICTORIA: Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我的前夫去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Since my husband's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现自己对超自然的故事更有兴趣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I find myself with more of a taste for supernatural fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很想念他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You must miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,非常想念\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 十分想念\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是鬼故事迷人之处 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And that's the charm of a ghost story, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不在于惊吓或恐怖 那些都是给小孩听的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not the scares and chills, that's just for children,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而是在于与自然世界之外产生联系的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but the hope of some contact with the great beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都希望能收到一点外界的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We all want some message from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是造物主最大的奥秘 让我们得不到慰藉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's the Creator's greatest mystery that we're allowed no such consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,逝者不能复生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The dead stay silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们只能等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and we must wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 开始讲故事吧 罗伯特爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come, begin your tale, Sir Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,气氛正合适呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's a chill in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,风正呼啸着穿越屋檐 给我们说点怪物的事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The wind is howling through the eaves. Tell us of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要出声\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们大喊大叫 他会把我们宰掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They said if we scream or shout, then he will slaughter us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但…他关在笼子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But he's in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个囚犯 他和我们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's a prisoner. He's the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他和我们不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's nothing like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那生物不是正常人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That creature is not mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,故事追溯到三百年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The story goes back 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,每到月圆之时 嚎叫之声就环绕着整个山谷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Every full moon, the howling rings through the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天早上 发现家畜被撕碎或生吞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Next morning, livestock is found ripped apart and devoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这些故事只是用来掩饰偷盗行为的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, tales like this just disguise the work of thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,偷了羊然后栽赃到狼身上 仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Steal the sheep and blame a wolf, simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但时常也会有小孩失踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ROBERT: But sometimes a child goes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,每一代里都会有一个男孩从家里消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Once in a generation, a boy will vanish from his homestead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别去 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ISOBEL: Don't, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要激怒他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't enrage him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你来自哪里 你不是地球物种\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where are you from? You're not from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你来自哪个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What planet are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里出生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where were you born?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这躯体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This body?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,十英里远\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ten miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一个懦弱痛苦的男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A weakling, heartsick boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在晚上被我的信徒偷走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}stolen away at night by the Brethren for my cultivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我挖走了他的灵魂 寄宿于他的心脏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I carved out his soul and sat in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有人描述过那生物吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are there descriptions of the creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 有的 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, yes, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有各种图画和木雕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Drawings and wood carvings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不仅仅是狼而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And it's not merely a wolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,比那严重得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个变成动物的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is a man who becomes an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这是人类的躯体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ROSE: All right, so the body's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢 里面的东西呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What about you, the thing inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,家乡如此遥远\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So far from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想回家 我们可以帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If you want to get back home, we can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why would I leave this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,工业世界 劳动力的世界 战争的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A world of industry, of workforce and warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我能够大有作为\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I could turn it to such purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我会转移到圣君身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I would migrate to the Holy Monarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指维多利亚女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You mean Queen Victoria?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只要咬一口 我就能进入她的血液\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}With one bite, I would pass into her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 狼的帝国就要开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And then it begins, the Empire of the Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,问这么多问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看 在你眼里 你也见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look! Inside your eyes. You've seen it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,见过什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Seen what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,狼 在你体内有着些与狼有关的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The wolf. There is something of the wolf about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你像太阳一样燃烧着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, you burn like the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但我所需要的是月亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but all I require is the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲认为这不只是个传说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My father didn't treat it as a story. He said it was fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他说那是个事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He said it was fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至主张和那怪物交流 了解它的企图\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He even claimed to have communed with the beast, to have learned its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我当初应该听他的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I should have listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他的工作被阻碍了 出现了敌对者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}His work was hindered. He made enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,圣凯瑟琳峡谷有一间寺庙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's a monastery in the Glen of St Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那里的信徒反对我父亲的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Brethren opposed my father's investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们认为他的工作违逆天意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Perhaps they thought his work ungodly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我当初也这么想 但是现在我怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's what I thought, but now I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这么做也许还有别的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What if they had a different reason for wanting the story kept quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们背离了上帝 而崇拜狼呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What if they turned from God and worshipped the wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们此刻正和我们在一起呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And what if they were with us right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,月光\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人 全都不要看他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All of you, stop looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,弗洛拉 不要看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Flora, don't look,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 抓紧铁链 然后拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}listen to me. Grab hold of the chain and pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 和我一起拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on, with me! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能 小姐 教徒禁止我们这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We can't, miss, we can't. The  Brethren forbid us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我说拉 别抱怨了 听我的 所有人都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I said pull! Stop your whining and listen to me! All of yous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也包括你 小姐 马上过来 拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And that means you, your Ladyship. Now, come on! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思 请做出解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What is the meaning of this? Explain yourself, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 他们抓了我的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry, Your Majesty, they've got my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯在哪 她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose, where's Rose? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特爵士 过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 快拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}...three, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一、二、三 拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}One, two, three, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 先生 我要求知道你的意图\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Tell me, sir. I demand to know your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,王座\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一、二、三 拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ROSE: ...two, three, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一、二、三\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}One, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Dull!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底死哪儿去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where the hell have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 漂亮极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, that's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们全都出去 走 走 走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get out, all of you! Come on! Out! Out! Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 看来你阻碍了火车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I take it, sir, that you halted my train
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了引我到这里来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}to bring me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等待这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We've waited so long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了等待你的的旅行碰上月圆之夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}for one of your journeys to coincide with the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就白等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then you have waited in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我这一生遭遇过六次暗杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}After six attempts on my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当然会有所准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I am hardly unprepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.81,0:23:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得你会开枪 女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, I don't think so, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的称呼应该是"陛下"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The correct form of address is "Your Majesty".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,带上武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,给我五支\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I need five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎贝尔夫人 带着姑娘们从厨房出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Lady Isobel, take the girls! Get them out through the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克森 做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Jackson, at arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能离开 你要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't leave you. What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要保护陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I must defend Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要担心我了 走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, don't think of me, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 都到我这儿来 过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All of you at my side! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是任何光线调节型物种\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Could be any form of light-modulating species
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可以被特定波长激活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}triggered by specific wavelengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它说过它想要什么没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did it say what it wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,王后 王冠 王座 你来说好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Queen, the crown, the throne, you name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,打不开 他们把我们锁在里面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It won't open. They've sealed us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.81,0:24:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 夫人 看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my lady, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.63,0:24:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会让我们出去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They'll never let us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.56,0:24:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们死定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They mean for us to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.82,0:24:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样说 弗洛拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't say that, Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.17,0:24:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 大伙们 我们撤退到楼上去 跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All right, you men, we should retreat upstairs. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.60,0:24:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会撤退 战斗结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll not retreat. The battle's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.82,0:24:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,天底下没有生物能抵挡住这样的袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's no creature on God's earth could survive such an assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说 快到楼上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm telling you, come upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And I'm telling you, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.23,0:24:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚要把这东西的皮挂到我墙壁上才睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I will sleep well tonight with that thing's hide upon my wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.41,0:25:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它一定在垂死挣扎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It must have crawled away to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.31,0:25:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.42,0:25:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.92,0:25:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们干掉它了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did they kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.22,0:25:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,靠过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.69,0:25:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特爵士 发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.36,0:25:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到很吵闹的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I heard such terrible noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.41,0:26:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 我们必须离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty, we've got to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,安杰洛神父怎么了 他还在那儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But what of Father Angelo, is he still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.89,0:26:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,雷诺斯队长在处理他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Captain Reynolds disposed of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.54,0:26:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,前门情况不好 堵住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The front door's no good. It's been boarded shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.32,0:26:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 陛下 你得爬窗户出去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pardon me, Your Majesty, you'll have to leg it out of a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.90,0:26:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请恕我不顾礼节 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse my manners, ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.70,0:26:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但请让我走在前边 这样更好的帮助陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but I shall go first, the better to assist Her Majesty's egress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.33,0:26:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,多么高尚的情操 罗伯特爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A noble sentiment, my Sir Walter Raleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.24,0:26:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能快点啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah, any chance you could hurry up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.96,0:26:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想让我们待在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I reckon the monky-boys want us to stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.19,0:26:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道我是谁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do they know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.91,0:26:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,知道 那就是为什么他们想要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah, that's why they want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.84,0:26:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,狼人把你困在这里是为了咬你一口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The wolf's lined you up for a biting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.47,0:26:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在别谈这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, stop this talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.65,0:26:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能真的有狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There can't be an actual wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.48,0:26:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们…跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We run.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.60,0:26:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.48,0:26:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没银子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You got any silver bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.60,0:26:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not on me, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.38,0:26:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这不就得了 我们跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There we are, then. We run.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.30,0:26:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 作为医生 我建议来场小跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty, as a doctor, I recommend a vigorous jog,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.36,0:27:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对身体有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}good for the health.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.17,0:27:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.87,0:27:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我守在这里拦住它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll take this position and hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.00,0:27:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们继续跑 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You keep moving, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.00,0:27:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 我查看了那件物品 它被人拿走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty, I went to look for the property and it was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.14,0:27:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,盒子是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The chest was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.31,0:27:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在我这里 它很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have it. It's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.75,0:27:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要好好的保重 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then remove yourself, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.23,0:27:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 你一定要保护好陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor, you stand as Her Majesty's protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.44,0:27:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你 罗伯特爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And you, Sir Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.45,0:27:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是皇室的叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're a traitor to the Crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.94,0:28:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹阻止不了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Bullets can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.53,0:28:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能给你们争取时间 马上跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They'll buy you time. Now, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.08,0:28:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,把门堵住\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Barricade the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.96,0:28:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下 嘘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Wait a minute. Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.13,0:28:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它停下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.15,0:29:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,它走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.82,0:29:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.85,0:29:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唯一的门吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is this the only door?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.71,0:29:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.17,0:29:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.43,0:29:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ROSE: Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.95,0:29:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 什么阻止了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't understand. What's stopping it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.91,0:29:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这房间里的某种东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Something inside this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.50,0:29:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么 为什么它不能进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What is it? Why can't it get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.75,0:30:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I tell you what, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.16,0:30:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.70,0:30:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.78,0:30:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.59,0:30:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.37,0:30:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.39,0:30:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.23,0:30:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该把你送走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I should have sent you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.02,0:30:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过暗示您这里有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I tried to suggest something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.94,0:30:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我指望您能察觉到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I thought you might notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.03,0:30:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得我的家丁有一点奇怪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did you think there was nothing strange about my household staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.95,0:30:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们全是光头 四肢发达\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, they were bald, athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.95,0:30:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子不在 我还以为你很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your wife's away, I just thought you were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.20,0:30:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便一提 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll tell you what though,, ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.37,0:30:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你现在并不觉得有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet you're not amused now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.14,0:30:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这很有趣吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you think this funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.31,0:30:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, ma'am, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.56,0:30:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么 我恳求哪个人来告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What, exactly, I pray, tell me, someone, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.75,0:30:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那个生物到底是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}what exactly is that creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.18,0:30:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能称之为狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You'd call it a werewolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.22,0:30:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但确切的说是狼型波长的混血人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but technically it's more of a lupine-wavelength haemovariform.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.98,0:30:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我该信任你吗 阁下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And should I trust you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.84,0:30:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你能这么轻易地改变口音\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You, who change your voice so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.70,0:30:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你的口音怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What happened to your accent?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.44,0:31:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 对了 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, right, sorry, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.78,0:31:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll not have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.63,0:31:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信你 不信那个生物 什么都不信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, sir. Not you, not that thing, none of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.07,0:31:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is not my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.47,0:31:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,槲寄生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mistletoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.20,0:31:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都戴着槲寄生花圈 狼人也不攻击他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They're all garlanded in mistletoe and the wolf doesn't attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谁把这个带到厨房来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who brought this into the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.43,0:31:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是那些信徒带进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Must have been the Brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.88,0:31:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,收集起来 快 每一残片都要 马上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gather it up, quickly. Every last scrap. Quick, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.81,0:31:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,槲寄生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mistletoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.50,0:31:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特爵士 那是你父亲放的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert, did your father put that there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.81,0:31:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 我想应该是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know. I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.86,0:31:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,另外一个门也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And on the other door, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.86,0:31:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是雕刻应该不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Though a carving wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.11,0:31:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.32,0:31:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,槲寄生 是槲寄生油\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Viscum album, the oil of the mistletoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.10,0:31:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,像油漆一样浸入木头里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's been worked into the wood like a varnish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.58,0:31:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲真聪明 我爱死他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How clever was your dad? I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.77,0:32:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,强大的生物 槲寄生 充满了凝血素和毒肽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Powerful stuff, mistletoe, bursting with lectins and viscotoxins.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.96,0:32:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且狼人对这个过敏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And the wolf's allergic to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.40,0:32:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或者它认为会过敏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Or it thinks it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.45,0:32:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那些光头僧侣需要一种控制狼人的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The monky-monk-monks need a way of controlling the wolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.21,0:32:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们训练它对特定的东西做出反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}maybe they trained it to react against certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.92,0:32:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 狼人并没打算放弃 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nevertheless, that creature won't give up, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.64,0:32:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们依然没有实在的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and we still don't possess an actual weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.32,0:32:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没继承到你父亲的智慧 是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, your father got all the brains, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.52,0:32:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,又开始没礼貌了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Being rude again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我正等你问呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good, I meant that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要武器 我们在书房里 书\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You want weapons? We're in a library. Books!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.39,0:32:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最好的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Best weapons in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.86,0:32:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这房间就是最好的军械库\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This room is the greatest arsenal we could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.98,0:32:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,武装自己吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Arm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.70,0:32:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没有狼的声音了 夫人 也许它走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's no sound of the wolf, my lady, perhaps it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.25,0:32:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,也许它在耍我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And perhaps it's toying with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.42,0:32:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But my husband's up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.96,0:32:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他还有任何活着的可能 我一定要帮他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and if there's any chance he's still alive, then, by God, I'll assist him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.63,0:32:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,查寻生物学和动物学\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look up biology and zoology.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.85,0:32:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,会有些关于狼的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There might be something on wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.95,0:32:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}DOCTOR: What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.95,0:32:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一本专门讲槲寄生的书\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A whole book on mistletoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.91,0:32:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,火药的应用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ROBERT: "The application of gunpowder..."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.83,0:32:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能制造炸药\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If we could build some form of explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.97,0:32:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hmm, that's the sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.33,0:33:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ohhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.31,0:33:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你老爸发现了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look what your old dad found.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.50,0:33:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,从天而降的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Something fell to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.03,0:33:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,太空船\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.09,0:33:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,流星\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Shooting star.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.73,0:33:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在基督1540年 詹姆斯五世统治时期\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}"In the year of our Lord 1540, under the reign of King James V,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.03,0:33:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有颗神奇的火球在深坑里燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}"an almighty fire did burn in the pit."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.09,0:33:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就在圣凯瑟琳峡谷 是那些僧侣地盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's the Glen of Saint Catherine, just by the monastery.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是三百年前的事了 它在等待什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But that's over 300 years ago. What's it been waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.92,0:33:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许只有一个细胞活下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe just a single cell survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.11,0:33:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一代一代缓慢适应着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Adapting slowly down the generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.97,0:33:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,它通过人类存活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it survived through the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.05,0:33:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,寄生在不同的人身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}host after host after host.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.95,0:33:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么它想要王座\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But why does it want the throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.57,0:33:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是它想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's what it wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.53,0:33:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,它是这么说的 "狼的帝国"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it said so. The Empire of the Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.26,0:33:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想像一下 如果维多利亚时代被加速\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Imagine it. The Victorian Age accelerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.64,0:33:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,烧煤的飞船和导弹 蒸汽驱动的机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Starships and missiles fuelled by coal and driven by steam,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.94,0:33:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,让历史在醒觉中崩溃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}leaving history devastated in its wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.36,0:33:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.62,0:33:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我死在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If I am to die here...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.19,0:33:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别那样说 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't say that, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.11,0:33:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿自杀也不让那畜生感染我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}...I would destroy myself rather than let that creature infect me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.55,0:34:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但那没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but that's no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.12,0:34:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要求你能找到某个安全的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I ask only that you find some place of safekeeping
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.80,0:34:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,来保存一个比我更久远 比我更珍贵的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}for something far older and more precious than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.65,0:34:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间去担心你的贵重物品了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hardly the time to worry about your valuables.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.58,0:34:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thank you for your opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.84,0:34:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有什么比这更有价值了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but there is nothing more valuable than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.97,0:34:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ROBERT: Oh, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.22,0:34:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那难道是科依诺尔钻石\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is that the Koh-i-noor?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.33,0:34:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.39,0:34:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最大的钻石\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The greatest diamond in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.74,0:34:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,作为战争战利品送到我手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Given to me as the spoils of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也许它的传说现在成真了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Perhaps its legend is now coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.55,0:34:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,传说拥有这钻石的人必死无疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It is said that whoever owns it must surely die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.88,0:34:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能等 什么都会成真\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, that's true of anything, if you wait long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.06,0:34:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我能否\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.81,0:34:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太美了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.40,0:34:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,它值多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How much is that worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.07,0:34:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,据说是 整个星球一周的工资\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They say, the wages of the entire planet for a whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.70,0:34:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还好我妈不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good job my mum's not here,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.63,0:35:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这个 她能赤手空拳单挑狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}she'd be fighting the wolf off with her bare hands for that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.27,0:35:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她一定会打赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And she'd win.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.83,0:35:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,狼人去哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where is the wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.52,0:35:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这股寂静令人怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't trust this silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.45,0:35:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么带着它旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why do you travel with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.19,0:35:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我每年都会朝圣一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My annual pilgrimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.92,0:35:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把它带给海勒和卡鲁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm taking it to Hellier and Carew,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.71,0:35:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,皇家珠宝匠 在海兹海德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the Royal Jewellers at Hazlehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.17,0:35:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这宝石需要重新切割\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The stone needs recutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.45,0:35:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但它很完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.64,0:35:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我前夫并不这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My late husband never thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.30,0:35:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,事实就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, there's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.91,0:35:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艾伯特王子不断地把这钻石拿去切割\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Prince Albert kept on having the Koh-i-noor cut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.29,0:35:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以前比这还大40% 但他从未满意过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It used to be 40% bigger than this, but he was never happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.12,0:35:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,继续切呀切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Kept on cutting and cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.08,0:35:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他总是说光泽不太对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He always said the shine was not quite right,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.61,0:35:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但他死时还没完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but he died with it still unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.97,0:35:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.04,0:35:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.54,0:35:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有好多未完成的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's a lot of unfinished business in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.25,0:35:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他父亲在研究 而你丈夫 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}His father's research and your husband, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.81,0:35:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他来这里探寻这颗钻石\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He came here and he sought the perfect diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.74,0:35:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold on, oh, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.98,0:35:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些零散的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All these separate things,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.32,0:35:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们根本不是零散的 它们相互联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}they're not separate at all, they're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.01,0:35:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我的头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}{\i1}Oh, my head, my head!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.17,0:36:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子 是为你设的陷阱 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What if this house... It's a trap for you. Is that right, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.88,0:36:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,显然\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.81,0:36:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,至少 狼人就是这么打算的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}At least, that's what the wolf intended,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.18,0:36:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果这是个陷阱中的陷阱呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but what if there's a trap inside the trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.51,0:36:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,解释一下 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Explain yourself, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.76,0:36:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他父亲和你丈夫 并不仅仅是在讲故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What if his father and your husband weren‘t just telling each other stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.92,0:36:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们大胆设想这些事都是真的 并且想了应对措施\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They dared to imagine all this was true, and they planned against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.01,0:36:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,设置了真正的陷阱 不是对你 而是对狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Laying the real trap not for you, but for the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.26,0:36:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那只狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That wolf, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.66,0:36:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出去 出去 出去 出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}DOCTOR: Out! Out! Out! Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.89,0:36:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.28,0:36:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,到天文台那里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We've got to get to the observatory!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.52,0:36:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,泼得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.02,0:36:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是槲寄生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}FLORA: It was mistletoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.21,0:36:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎贝尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Isobel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:36:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,马上回到楼下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}ROBERT: Now get back downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.69,0:36:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,保护好自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Keep yourself safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.75,0:37:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My love. Now, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.68,0:37:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘们 跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Girls, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.93,0:37:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,到楼下去 回到厨房 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Down the back stairs back to the kitchens, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.31,0:37:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.93,0:37:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天文台在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The observatory is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.72,0:37:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有槲寄生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No mistletoe on these doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.32,0:37:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你父亲希望狼人进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}'cause your father wanted the wolf to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.93,0:37:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要时间 这儿没有什么可以做屏障吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I just need time. Is there any way of barricading this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.85,0:37:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你做你的事 我来抵抗它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do your work, and I'll defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.25,0:37:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能用绳子或什么把这里封住\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If we could bind them shut with rope or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.98,0:37:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 我给你争取时间 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I said I'll find you time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.60,0:37:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 快点进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.67,0:37:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.86,0:37:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 钻石\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty, the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.17,0:37:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用来做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.29,0:37:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这钻石最初的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The purpose it was designed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.02,0:37:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.56,0:37:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,升起它 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Lift it, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.10,0:38:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是看星星的好时机啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not the right time for stargazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.09,0:38:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,正是时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.87,0:38:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我因为你犯了叛国罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I committed treason for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.79,0:38:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我的妻子 会记住我的荣誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but now my wife will remember me with honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.87,0:38:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我是信仰的捍卫者 信仰也会捍卫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I am the Defender of the Faith, and that Faith shall defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.64,0:38:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,记得你说过这是坏的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You said this thing doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.15,0:38:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,作为望远镜它是坏的 但它根本不是望远镜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It doesn't work as a telescope, 'cause that's not what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.34,0:38:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是储光室 它能放大光线 如同武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's a light chamber. It magnifies the light, like a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.41,0:38:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只需要把它充充能量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We've just got to power it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用什么 这里没有电\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}With what? There's no electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.28,0:38:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,月光\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.38,0:38:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但狼人需要月光 它是月光组成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But the wolf needs moonlight. It's made by moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.56,0:38:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你70%的成分是水 但你照样会淹死 加油\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're 70% water, you can still drown. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.23,0:39:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.79,0:39:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让它再亮点 让我走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Make it brighter. Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.13,0:40:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.88,0:40:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它咬到你了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did it bite you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.30,0:40:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 只是割伤 就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, it's... It's a cut, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.28,0:40:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那东西咬了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If that thing bit you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.02,0:40:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只是门裂开时的小木片弄的 没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was a splinter of wood when the door came apart. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.69,0:40:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.59,0:40:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.66,0:40:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,由教会和国家授予我的权力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}By the power invested in me by the Church and the State,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.23,0:41:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我封你为塔迪斯博士爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I dub thee Sir Doctor of Tardis.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.21,0:41:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,由教会和国家授予我的权力 我封你为\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}By the power invested in me by the Church and the State,I dub thee
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍威尔庄园的洛斯女爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Dame Rose of the Powell Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.38,0:41:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You may stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.39,0:41:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Many thanks, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.18,0:41:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.83,0:41:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,回到家他们一定不会相信我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They're never gonna believe this back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.44,0:41:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 昨晚你说到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your Majesty, you said last night
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.31,0:41:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,收不到来自世界之外的讯息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}about receiving no message from the great beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.77,0:41:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你丈夫切割钻石是为了救你的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think your husband cut that diamond to save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.77,0:41:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他到现在还在天堂守护着你 陛下 \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's protecting you even now, ma'am, from beyond the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.65,0:41:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你也可以考虑一下这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then you may think on this also,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.06,0:41:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这并不好笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that I am not amused.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.37,0:41:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.74,0:41:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不好笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not remotely amused.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.79,0:41:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今后 我要放逐你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And henceforth, I banish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.21,0:41:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.32,0:41:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经奖赏过你们 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have rewarded you, Sir Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.26,0:41:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你们要离开大英帝国 永远不得返回\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and now you are exiled from this Empire, never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.55,0:42:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你们是谁 或从哪来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know what you are, the two of you, or where you're from,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.43,0:42:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道你们和星空与魔法结交 并觉得那很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but I know that you consort with stars and magic, and think it fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.65,0:42:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们的世界在恐惧、亵渎、和死亡颠峰上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But your world is steeped in terror and blasphemy and death,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.17,0:42:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会允许的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and I will not allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.28,0:42:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要离开这些土地 希望你们会反省\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You will leave these shores, and you will reflect, I hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.28,0:42:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们漂流时背离正道有多远\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}on how you came to stray so far from all that is good,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.50,0:42:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你们能在这些骇人生活中生存多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and how much longer you may survive this terrible life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.46,0:42:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,马上离开我的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now leave my world,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.80,0:42:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要再回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.01,0:42:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.99,0:42:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.52,0:42:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Walk on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.10,0:42:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, but the funny thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.88,0:42:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,维多利亚的血液确实发生了突变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Queen Victoria actually did suffer a mutation of the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.48,0:42:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是历史事实 她是血友病患者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's historical record. She was haemophiliac.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.13,0:42:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,人们曾把那叫做皇家病\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They used to call it the Royal Disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.74,0:42:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那一直是个谜 因为她不是遗传得到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but it's always been a mystery because she didn't inherit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.07,0:42:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她父亲也没有 她母亲也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Her mum didn't have it. Her dad didn't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.78,0:42:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样凭空出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It came from nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.76,0:42:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说那是狼人咬的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What, and you're saying that's a wolf bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.51,0:43:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也许血友病只是一种委婉的称呼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, maybe haemophilia is just a Victorian euphemism.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.75,0:43:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,狼人的婉称\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}For werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.73,0:43:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.16,0:43:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,维多利亚女王是狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Queen Victoria's a werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.43,0:43:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.19,0:43:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她的孩子也得了皇家病\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And her children had the Royal Disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.84,0:43:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她小咬了一下他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe she gave them a quick nip.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.13,0:43:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么王室家族都是狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So the Royal Family are werewolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.68,0:43:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 也许现在还不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, maybe not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.04,0:43:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一个狼人细胞可能需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean, a single wolf cell could take
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.46,0:43:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一百多年才能成熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}100 years to mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.62,0:43:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可能要到…21世纪初期\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Might be ready by, oh, early 21st century.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.56,0:43:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 太扯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, that's just ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.43,0:43:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,注意 安妮公主\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mind you, Princess Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.08,0:43:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不多说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.77,0:43:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你仔细想想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And if you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.19,0:43:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们确实非常私密\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}they're very private.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.75,0:43:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是预先计划好一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They plan everything in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.53,0:43:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能真的按月亮来算时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They could schedule themselves around the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.80,0:43:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谁也说不准\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We'd never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.15,0:43:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 他们喜欢打猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And they like hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.89,0:43:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们爱好血腥的运动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They love blood sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.48,0:43:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐 他们是狼人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God! They're werewolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.55,0:43:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什么 你会留在这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What will you do? Will you stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.72,0:44:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为我能留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't think I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.93,0:44:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我会卖掉它 或者拆掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'd sell it, or pull this place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.39,0:44:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我们不会公开这见事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Although we may not speak of these events in public,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.41,0:44:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但它们不会被遗忘的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}they will not be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.99,0:44:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.57,0:44:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫的牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your husband's sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.31,0:44:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他父亲的天才\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the ingenuity of his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.82,0:44:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会永远长存\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}they will live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.08,0:44:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但怎么做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.24,0:44:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚 我看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I saw, last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.14,0:44:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大不列颠存在着各种难以想像的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that Great Britain has enemies beyond imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.77,0:44:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须全面保护我们的边界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and we must defend our borders on all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.84,0:44:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我提议建立一个机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I propose an institute
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.11,0:44:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,专门研究这些奇怪的事件 并与之做斗争\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}to investigate these strange happenings and to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.35,0:44:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会这机构命名为"火炬木"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I would call it Torchwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.05,0:44:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,火炬木研究院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Torchwood Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.44,0:44:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个博士再回来 那么他得小心点了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And if this Doctor should return, then he should beware,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.48,0:44:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为火炬木在等着他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}because Torchwood will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.16,0:45:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 同学们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good morning, class.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.68,0:45:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都坐好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are we sitting comfortably?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.91,0:45:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,三个月前 厨房所有东西都被替换掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Three months ago, turns out all the kitchen staff were replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.94,0:45:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看 有些事情在发生着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}See? There's definitely something going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.33,0:45:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你回来果然是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was right to call you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.26,0:45:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我为你介绍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}May I introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.36,0:45:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉·简·史密斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Miss Sarah Jane Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.56,0:45:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.31,0:45:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.15,0:45:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 非常高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.19,0:45:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你在上班时间不可以随意离开你的岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You are not permitted to leave your station during a sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.64,0:45:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,班里的男生懂得远超地球水平的知识\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Boy in class this morning, got knowledge way beyond planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.72,0:45:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,K-9\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}K9!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.35,0:45:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的时间到了 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Our time has come, my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.65,0:45:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们将成为神\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs13\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Today we shall become gods.
